"title": "5779: advice",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5779",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Counsel is essential for gaining wisdom, though human advice is not always reliable. God's advice is necessary and trustworthy for guidance in life.</p>\n<h2>Human advice</h2>\n<h3>A wise person seeks advice from others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:15\">PRO 12:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:14\">PRO 11:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:10\">PRO 13:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:12\">PRO 15:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:22\">PRO 15:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:20\">PRO 19:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:6\">PRO 24:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:9\">PRO 27:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl4:13\">ECC 4:13</a></p>\n<h3>Rejecting good advice can lead to disaster</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:30-Prov1:31\">PRO 1:30–1:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs12:8\">1KI 12:8</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr10:8\">2CH 10:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs12:13-1Kgs12:15\">1KI 12:13–12:15</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr10:13-2Chr10:15\">2CH 10:13–10:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:25-Prov1:26\">PRO 1:25–1:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer18:18\">JER 18:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:11\">ACT 27:11</a></p>\n<h3>Human advice can have unseen dangers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:5\">PRO 12:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job21:16\">JOB 21:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps1:1\">PSA 1:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:11\">ISA 19:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek11:2\">EZK 11:2</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of good human advice</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod18:17-Exod18:24\">EXO 18:17–18:24</a> <em>Jethro</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam17:5-2Sam17:16\">2SA 17:5–17:16</a> <em>Hushai</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:13-Esth1:22\">EST 1:13–1:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth2:1-Esth2:4\">EST 2:1–2:4</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:27\">DAN 4:27</a> <em>Daniel</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:38\">ACT 5:38</a> <em>Gamaliel</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:10\">2CO 8:10</a> <em>Paul</em></p>\n<h2>Examples of bad human advice</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:15-Num31:16\">NUM 31:15–31:16</a> <em>Balaam</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam15:31-2Sam15:34\">2SA 15:31–15:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam16:20-2Sam16:23\">2SA 16:20–16:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam17:1-2Sam17:4\">2SA 17:1–17:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam17:21-2Sam17:23\">2SA 17:21–17:23</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs12:28\">1KI 12:28</a> <em>Jeroboam</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:11\">ISA 19:11</a> <em>Egyptian advisers</em></p>\n<h2>Seeking advice from false gods is futile</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:31\">LEV 19:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut18:14\">DEU 18:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr25:15-2Chr25:16\">2CH 25:15–25:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:3\">ISA 19:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:28-Isa41:29\">ISA 41:28–41:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa47:12-Isa47:13\">ISA 47:12–47:13</a></p>\n<h2>God needs no-one to advise him</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:13-Isa40:14\">ISA 40:13–40:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job12:13\">JOB 12:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:14\">PRO 8:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:29\">ISA 28:29</a></p>\n<h2>God gives advice</h2>\n<h3>To his people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:8\">PSA 32:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps16:7\">PSA 16:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:24\">PSA 73:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:18\">REV 3:18</a></p>\n<h3>Through Jesus Christ and his Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:2\">ISA 11:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:6\">ISA 9:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:26\">JHN 14:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:26\">JHN 15:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:13\">JHN 16:13</a></p>\n<h3>Through his word</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:16\">2TI 3:16</a></strong></p>\n<h2>God frustrates bad advice</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:19\">1CO 1:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam17:14\">2SA 17:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:10\">PSA 33:10</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of receiving God's advice</h2>\n<p>David:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam23:1-1Sam23:4\">1SA 23:1–23:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam2:1\">2SA 2:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:5\">1KI 22:5</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr18:4\">2CH 18:4</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of rejecting God's advice</h2>\n<p>Job:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:2\">JOB 38:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job42:2-Job42:3\">JOB 42:2–42:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:13\">PSA 106:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:11\">PSA 107:11</a></p>",
